	<sect2>
		<title>MEGA and Mumps Compiler</title>
		<para>Mumps Compiler is a compiler for a subset of the Mumps language, a language used mainly in health care. It is compatible with most operating systems with a standard C compiler. License: GPL <ulink url="http://home.clara.net/finch/"> OMEGA</ulink> is an Open Source implementation of the M-Technology (MUMPS) programming language. It is extendable, and currently embedded with MySQL; it is ideal as a trigger/validation frontend to SQL. License: free for non-commercial use.
		</para>
	</sect2>

